                  , was at the same Session, ordered to be transported to the said coast of New South Wales, or some one or other of the islands adjacent, for and during the term of his natural life, pursuant to the Statute, &amp;c.; and that he afterwards, on the <rs id="t18300708-2-cd11" type="crimeDate">28th of June</rs>
